snippet.title: Arcade Game: Swinging Singles [Edited & Censored] (1983 Ent., Limited)
snippet.description:
Another porn game released in the arcades where you driving around the maze while avoid the cops. Then you must go to the orgy house to find a key to open the door to have intercourse with a prostitute. Game is very similar Atari 2600's X-man. 

It's very shocking to see that MAME can emulator porn games released in the arcades. 

Note: Due to the graphic nature of this game and since this game contains adult content, the video is heavily edited and censored. So the explicit content such as the nudity in the sex scene has been blocked in order to comply with YouTube's community guidelines

I noticed that parts of the bottom video is cut and it seems mame internal AVI output did not record this game properly.
